Test2/Pod version 0.01
=====================

This library's module, Test2::Pod, provides an interface for validating POD in
module files with Test2.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

Dependencies
------------

Test2::Pod requires the following modules:

* Pod::Simple 3.05
* Test2::Suite 0.000126
* File::Spec

